For testing, research, analysis, and product development, including to develop and improve our Website, products, and services.
To respond to law enforcement requests and as required by applicable law, court order, or governmental regulations.
As described to you when collecting your personal information or as otherwise set forth in the CCPA.
To evaluate or conduct a merger, divestiture, restructuring, reorganization, dissolution, or other sale or transfer of some or all of MobilityWare’s assets, whether as a going concern or as part of bankruptcy, liquidation, or similar proceeding, in which personal information held by MobilityWare about our Website users is among the assets transferred.
